<item>
  <title>Ecuaciones que uso seguido</title>
  <link>https://diezvariante.cl/blog/posts/ecuaciones-utiles/</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 





<p>Un post de referencia personal. Lo actualizo cuando aparece algo que vale la pena anotar.</p>
<section id="cálculo" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="cálculo">Cálculo</h2>
<p><strong>Regla de la cadena:</strong></p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cfrac%7Bd%7D%7Bdx%7D%5Bf(g(x))%5D%20=%20f'(g(x))%20%5Ccdot%20g'(x)"></p>
<p><strong>Integral por partes:</strong></p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cint%20u%20%5C,%20dv%20=%20uv%20-%20%5Cint%20v%20%5C,%20du"></p>
<p><strong>Serie de Taylor</strong> alrededor de <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?a">:</p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?f(x)%20=%20%5Csum_%7Bn=0%7D%5E%7B%5Cinfty%7D%20%5Cfrac%7Bf%5E%7B(n)%7D(a)%7D%7Bn!%7D(x-a)%5En"></p>
</section>
<section id="álgebra-lineal" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="álgebra-lineal">Álgebra lineal</h2>
<p>El <strong>determinante</strong> de una matriz <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?2%20%5Ctimes%202">:</p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cdet%5Cbegin%7Bpmatrix%7D%20a%20&amp;%20b%20%5C%5C%20c%20&amp;%20d%20%5Cend%7Bpmatrix%7D%20=%20ad%20-%20bc"></p>
<p>La solución de <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?A%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%20=%20%5Cmathbf%7Bb%7D"> existe y es única cuando <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cdet(A)%20%5Cneq%200">:</p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%20=%20A%5E%7B-1%7D%5Cmathbf%7Bb%7D"></p>
<p><strong>Norma euclidiana</strong> de un vector <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathbf%7Bv%7D%20=%20(v_1,%20%5Cldots,%20v_n)">:</p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5C%7C%5Cmathbf%7Bv%7D%5C%7C%20=%20%5Csqrt%7B%5Csum_%7Bi=1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20v_i%5E2%7D"></p>
</section>
<section id="probabilidad" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="probabilidad">Probabilidad</h2>
<p><strong>Teorema de Bayes:</strong></p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?P(A%20%5Cmid%20B)%20=%20%5Cfrac%7BP(B%20%5Cmid%20A)%5C,%20P(A)%7D%7BP(B)%7D"></p>
<p><strong>Esperanza</strong> de una variable discreta:</p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathbb%7BE%7D%5BX%5D%20=%20%5Csum_%7Bx%7D%20x%20%5Ccdot%20P(X%20=%20x)"></p>
<p><strong>Distribución normal</strong> <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?X%20%5Csim%20%5Cmathcal%7BN%7D(%5Cmu,%20%5Csigma%5E2)">:</p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?f(x)%20=%20%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5Csigma%5Csqrt%7B2%5Cpi%7D%7D%20%5Cexp%5C!%5Cleft(-%5Cfrac%7B(x%20-%20%5Cmu)%5E2%7D%7B2%5Csigma%5E2%7D%5Cright)"></p>
</section>
<section id="código-de-ejemplo" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="código-de-ejemplo">Código de ejemplo</h2>
<p>Calcular la norma de un vector en Python:</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb1" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode python code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb1-1"><span class="im" style="color: #00769E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">import</span> numpy <span class="im" style="color: #00769E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">as</span> np</span>
<span id="cb1-2"></span>
<span id="cb1-3">v <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> np.array([<span class="fl" style="color: #AD0000;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">3.0</span>, <span class="fl" style="color: #AD0000;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">4.0</span>])</span>
<span id="cb1-4">norma <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> np.linalg.norm(v)  <span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;"># → 5.0</span></span>
<span id="cb1-5"><span class="bu" style="color: null;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">print</span>(<span class="ss" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">f"‖v‖ = </span><span class="sc" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">{</span>norma<span class="sc" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">}</span><span class="ss" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"</span>)</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>Y lo mismo desde cero sin NumPy:</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb2" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode python code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb2-1"><span class="im" style="color: #00769E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">import</span> math</span>
<span id="cb2-2"></span>
<span id="cb2-3"><span class="kw" style="color: #003B4F;
background-color: null;
font-weight: bold;
font-style: inherit;">def</span> norma(v: <span class="bu" style="color: null;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">list</span>[<span class="bu" style="color: null;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">float</span>]) <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-&gt;</span> <span class="bu" style="color: null;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">float</span>:</span>
<span id="cb2-4">    <span class="cf" style="color: #003B4F;
background-color: null;
font-weight: bold;
font-style: inherit;">return</span> math.sqrt(<span class="bu" style="color: null;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">sum</span>(x<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">**</span><span class="dv" style="color: #AD0000;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">2</span> <span class="cf" style="color: #003B4F;
background-color: null;
font-weight: bold;
font-style: inherit;">for</span> x <span class="kw" style="color: #003B4F;
background-color: null;
font-weight: bold;
font-style: inherit;">in</span> v))</span>
<span id="cb2-5"></span>
<span id="cb2-6"><span class="bu" style="color: null;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">print</span>(norma([<span class="dv" style="color: #AD0000;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">3</span>, <span class="dv" style="color: #AD0000;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">4</span>]))  <span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;"># 5.0</span></span></code></pre></div></div>


</section>

 ]]></description>
